You need a vps, 2500 BRO and a full synced windows wallet
First create a new BRO address with "getnewaddress <label for node>" Second send 2500 Coins to the new address "sendtoaddress <address generated> 2500" after that wait for 10+ confirmations Third get you outputs with"masternode outputs" Fourthly get you genkey with "masternode genkey"
